title: Great app
text: I’ve tried many different video editing apps. I’m pretty new to creating videos for social but this is definitely the easiest to use and so worth it! I used the free version without any issues for a couple months and then decided the pro was worth it for me since I’m doing much more video editing lately. The only thing I wish was better is I wish that projects were more easily shared between devices. I have CapCut on iPhone, tablet, and desktop, but the projects started on each device don’t immediately transfer to the others. Other than that, I love the app :)
